      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ") often denote the winning over of souls for themselves or others. Wetstein and Loesner, Hemsterhusius, ad Lucian. Dial. Mort. viii.; Burmann, ad Phaedr. iv. 4. Comp. on ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
